## Moving All Items in the Array

### Question

Write a function that moves every element in an array to the right by `N` positions.

### Answer:
```javascript
    function reverse\(arr: any[], moving\: number \)\) {
    for \(var i = 0; i < moving; ++i\){
        // still moving elements to the right
    }

    for \(var j = 0; j < arr.length - moving; ++j\){
        arr[j] = arr[j + moving];
    }

    for \(var k = arr.length - 1; k > arr.length - moving; --k\){
        arr[k] = arr[k - moving];
    }
    }
```
